76561198091838988,Recommended,266010,14436686,"Posted: 11 February, 2015",all,Amirani  Unbound,"This is a fun and inexpensive logic puzzler.  The gameplay is basic and increasing in difficulty as you unlock the latter levels. The player must connect the lines without intersecting, unless through a junction box, to go from a start place to the end place.  All pieces must be connected and in some instances a certain number of intersections must occur through junction boxes.  There is also a dailly puzzle generator that can be used to generate puzzles of differing difficulties randomly each day.Achievements are based upon completing sets of 25 puzzles.  There are 26 sets going from A-Z with an achievement for each one plus achievements for doing certain amounts of dailly puzzles. An achievement is also given for opening different color pallets.  Which are opened by completing puzzles.My personal experience of the gameplay it was fun right at first.  Then got a lil old, but, I was glad I stuck with it because over time my mind seemed to become more attuned to how the lines had to flow in order to complete the puzzles."
