,Recommended,266010,9605780,"Posted: 23 March, 2014",all,PIXELMONARCH,"When I have found LYNE on Steam, I instantly fall inlove with the graphics, simple and clean, but yet interesting. So I bought it (at the moment 1,99€ at Steam)The gameplay is easy, you click & hold at the first main symbol (these with border & filling) and lead the way to the other main symbol of the same kind. Done. You can not cross a way twice. Thats the main idea, kind of like the old game most of you played in school ""Dots & Boxes"". As probably every game in this world, it get's harder and harder from level to level. After 25 Levels you gain a triangle and finished the sets just to unlock another one.If you unlocked all sets, don't worry, after set B you unlock the ability to play daily sets. Every day you will get new sets with random difficulties to play and win.ReviewDesign:I love the design. It is simple and clean, very interesting and smooth to watch. Sadly this game does not support HD/Full-HD on PC, so that some of the athmosphere gets lost. Also it's kind of unsharp in the fonts sometimes7/10Music & Audio:The music theme of the game at all is awesome and relaxing. The sounds when you finish a level are great and make you happy, so you get addicted in unlocking more levels. The variety of the music is sadly pretty small and the sound of the symbols when you pass them sound like if someone is blowing into a bottle of Coca Cola and gets annoying after a while.6/10Gameplay & Addiction:Clearly it is a very great gameplay if you love that kind of ""strategy"" games. It combines oldschool elements with some new interesting features. Also the veriety of levels and the daily feature is great. Sometimes the balance of the levels is pretty uneven, as example Level B18 was super hard while the next few levels where pretty easy. Fix the balance a little bit ande this would be amazing9/10Cost-Benefit Equation & resumé:If you plan to play this game on the computer I can just highly recommend you this game. But!: Be aware, if you look for some super sexy time killer, you will just get pleased in the time killer part, 'cause the fact that this game is not HD/Full-HD is very sad, 'cause the pretty design gets lost in unrendered and unsharp fonts. Still every little design element is perfectly planned through and don't hurt your eyes at all.For the cheap price of 2.99€ (1.99€ in sale at the moment!) you get more than you can ask. Sell some of your useless DotA2/TF2/CS:GO stuff and buy this game.Thank you! If you like this review, you can feel free to add me on Steam"
