,Recommended,266010,13207424,"Posted: 2 December, 2014",all,Nyc2x,"Simple to understand, harder to solve. If you like relaxing but challenging puzzle games with many levels (from A to Z + daily levels), you should definitely try out this one.Each level presents a grid of triangles, diamonds and squares of (initially) various pastel colours, along with a few octagonal junction boxes. Draw a line connecting all of the shapes with the heavier-bordered end blocks. Each connecting line only once and touch each shape only once, and have to pass through each junction a set number of times.Game: 8.0/10Graphic: 8.5/10100% Achievement :Easy| Medium | Hard | Very Hard"
,Recommended,266010,22846503,"Posted: 7 May, 2016",all,ุ,"A simple, yet stylish way to enhance your profile ||An exceptional puzzle game that has the right difficulty curve, addictive gameplay and a amazing minimalist design. To put the icing on the cake it has easy achievements which can be used to spell what you'd like using the achievement showcase. You also get 3/5 card drops for playing.||LYNE has hours of relaxing content with 650 puzzles to solve and the additon of 50 daily puzzles. Not to mention that it also has a soothing, dynamic sound track which works well with the simplistic visuals. The objective of LYNE is simple; Try to connect A to B without intersecting the other lines and fulfilling the requirements to complete the level. After completing all the levels in a set, you will unlock an achievement plus another set. After a while you will also unlock different colour palettes as an added bonus for completing sets. The puzzles start to get harder as you continue through the game as the puzzles are more complex and new mechanics are introduced, however the game does get repetitve at times, despite the difficulty curve. ||To sum it up, this is a great game to kill some time or to play whilst watching something. It's pretty cheap too, and you can find a 50% off coupon somewhere, but is well worth the full price in my opinion."
