,Recommended,266010,17415369,"Posted: 6 August, 2015",all,Gamecool 10,"What is LYNE?LYNE is a unique little puzzle game where you match lines through similarly colored shapes. Seems easy right? After passing through the first levels, things get increasingly more challenging. More shapes, a new object that allows multiple lines to pass through, (Called a multicell) and more!The game is extremely simplistic, with no background music, singularly colored shapes, and a simple background. (Which can be changed to different colors depending on how far you are in the game) This isn't a bad thing though, LYNE is more for the fellows who want a nice, little, relaxing puzzle game."
