,Recommended,266010,20387520,"Posted: 7 January, 2016",all,KameHawk,"LYNE is a nice casual puzzle game. Each puzzle is satisfying to complete and does not stress you out when trying to solve it. You try to connect multiple colored points together through ""connector"" points. Each connector point has a certain amount of times you can drag a line through it. You need to connect all the reds, blue, or yellow points together, while filling up the number of times you can pass through the connector points. It is not difficult and difficult at the same time. Give it a try.Also, it comes with 20 cent worth cards and each achievement looks like a letter, so you can spell something out on your achievement showcase."
