,Recommended,266010,19353540,"Posted: 28 November, 2015",all,=(e)= a tiny cactus,"Sure, this game is pretty repetetive. Sure, it gives you achievements that are letters so you can write your name on your profile. But while those things are true, for $2.99 (or $0.89 during the steam sales) you can't get a much better game. It's fun, it's simple, it's addicting, and it genuinely challenges your brain regardless of how simple it seems. At the beginning of the game, it's very simple. It just gets harder and harder from there.Pros- Simple gameplay- Tough puzzles- Very casual, easy to kick back and play- Challeges your brain real good- Infinite puzzles, since there are new level packs literally every day, not to mention the 650 built in levels (26 packs, 25 levels each). At $2.99, that's 217 levels per dollar, which is irrelevant if you do the daily puzzle packs which just keep coming.- Even for full price, it's a really good deal for any puzzle fan- Beautiful art styleCons- If you don't like puzzles it will be painful for you- Boolean volume control. If you want to turn the game volume down, either turn it off or go to the volume mixer.I would definitely recommend it if you have a bit of extra cash. I drank an Arnold Palmer and had to pee really bad for like 2 hours, but ignored it and kept playing. It's too fun.10/10."
,Recommended,266010,27347930,"Posted: 24 November, 2016",all,katpotts,"LYNE is a great relaxing puzzle game and a perfect time waster. Building on the line puzzle genre LYNE invites players into a menagerie of well designed short puzzles, around 30 minutes too 2 minutes for most. The puzzles start out simple enough, at first just dealing with connecting A to B, but with Witness-esque mechanics gradually introduced as the player progresses so you'll soon start to deal with some real brain ticklers. The visual and audio design of this game is top notch too, simple and clean visuals with soothing tones, the only thing that is lacking would be music.Overall a well designed, simple yet clever puzzle game."
